ic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1462aac0 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"1462aac0\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1bd13710 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1bd13710\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Frequently Asked Questions<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fe05be7 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"fe05be7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-73261d58 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"73261d58\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>when selection the filling system for your lipstick products,each of these systems typically supports a range of container sizes, viscosities, and formulations, ensuring compatibility with traditional bullet lipsticks, slim sticks, tubes, and jars. Whether you\u2019re scaling up a classic lipstick line or branching into nourishing balms and vibrant glosses, there\u2019s a filling machine engineered to optimize your production process.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-48395f6d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"48395f6d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-71831554 elementor-widget elementor-widget-n-accordion\" data-id=\"71831554\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;default_state&quot;:&quot;expanded&quot;,&quot;max_items_expended&quot;:&quot;one&quot;,&quot;n_accordion_animation_duration&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;ms&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:400,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]}}\" data-widget_type=\"nested-accordion.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-n-accordion\" aria-label=\"Accordion. Open links with Enter or Space, close with Escape, and navigate with Arrow Keys\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<details id=\"e-n-accordion-item-1900\" class=\"e-n-accordion-item\" open>\n\t\t\t\t<summary class=\"e-n-accordion-item-title\" data-accordion-index=\"1\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"e-n-accordion-item-1900\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><h2 class=\"e-n-accordion-item-title-text\"> What's the filling technology adapted for filling lipstick? <\/h2><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>\n\t\t\t<span class='e-opened' ><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-fas-minus\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z\"><\/path><\/svg><\/span>\n\t\t\t<span class='e-closed'><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-fas-plus\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z\"><\/path><\/svg><\/span>\n\t\t<\/span>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/summary>\n\t\t\t\t<div role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"e-n-accordion-item-1900\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5adec2aa e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5adec2aa\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-14734756 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"14734756\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A piston volumetric filling system is adapted for filling the lipstick. Servo-driven nozzles deliver 0.1ml accuracy through volumetric displacement, ensuring consistent product weight and minimal waste. Pressure sensors maintain stable flow, while anti-drip valves close within milliseconds.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/details>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<details id=\"e-n-accordion-item-1901\" class=\"e-n-accordion-item\" >\n\t\t\t\t<summary class=\"e-n-accordion-item-title\" data-accordion-index=\"2\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"e-n-accordion-item-1901\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><h2 class=\"e-n-accordion-item-title-text\"> What accessories or auxiliary machines are offered for cosmetic manufacturing lines? <\/h2><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>\n\t\t\t<span class='e-opened' ><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-fas-minus\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z\"><\/path><\/svg><\/span>\n\t\t\t<span class='e-closed'><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-fas-plus\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z\"><\/path><\/svg><\/span>\n\t\t<\/span>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/summary>\n\t\t\t\t<div role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"e-n-accordion-item-1901\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-92aef1f e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"92aef1f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"e-n-accordion-item-1901\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ca65ec5 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"ca65ec5\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a5c159a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a5c159a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Essential Auxiliary Equipment for Cosmetic Manufacturing<\/h3><p><br \/>In addition to the core lipstick filling machines, a range of specialized auxiliary equipment is available to optimize your entire cosmetic production line. These solutions ensure seamless processing, whether you&#8217;re crafting classic lipsticks, powders, or innovative beauty formulas:<\/p><h3>Compacting and Powder Processing:<\/h3><p>Integrate machines such as powder compactors, mixers, sifters, and pulverizers for smooth, consistent formulation of pressed powders and blushes. Brands like IKA and Hosokawa Micron are industry favorites for these tasks.<\/p><h3><br \/>Precision Filling Solutions:<\/h3><p>From CC creams and mascaras to lip balms, glosses, oils, and nail polish, there are specific filling machines tailored to each viscosity and packaging type. Volumetric piston and gear pump technologies deliver precise dosing regardless of the formulation.<\/p><h3>Efficient Cooling and Finishing:<\/h3><p>Cooling tunnels manage product temperature post-filling, ensuring structural integrity and accelerated set times. Three-roll mills are invaluable for creating ultra-smooth, homogenous textures in creams and pastes.<\/p><h3>Versatile Packaging and Sealing:<\/h3><p>Tube filling and sealing systems, compatible with brands like Norden and IWK, make packaging a breeze across various product lines, while soap forming and pen-filling machines expand your portfolio possibilities.<br \/>Daily Chemical and Skincare Support: Dedicated filling lines for skincare lotions, serums, and fragrance products enable flexible, multi-product manufacturing.<\/p><p>When building out your cosmetic facility, these auxiliary machines allow you to scale, customize, and streamline production\u2014from raw material handling to finished packaging\u2014all while maintaining quality and efficiency.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/details>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<script type=\"application\/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https:\\\/\\\/schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What's the filling technology adapted for filling lipstick?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"A piston volumetric filling system is adapted for filling the lipstick. Servo-driven nozzles deliver 0.1ml accuracy through volumetric displacement, ensuring consistent product weight and minimal waste. Pressure sensors maintain stable flow, while anti-drip valves close within milliseconds.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What accessories or auxiliary machines are offered for cosmetic manufacturing lines?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Essential Auxiliary Equipment for Cosmetic ManufacturingIn addition to the core lipstick filling machines, a range of specialized auxiliary equipment is available to optimize your entire cosmetic production line. These solutions ensure seamless processing, whether you&#8217;re crafting classic lipsticks, powders, or innovative beauty formulas:Compacting and Powder Processing:Integrate machines such as powder compactors, mixers, sifters, and pulverizers for smooth, consistent formulation of pressed powders and blushes. Brands like IKA and Hosokawa Micron are industry favorites for these tasks.Precision Filling Solutions:From CC creams and mascaras to lip balms, glosses, oils, and nail polish, there are specific filling machines tailored to each viscosity and packaging type. Volumetric piston and gear pump technologies deliver precise dosing regardless of the formulation.Efficient Cooling and Finishing:Cooling tunnels manage product temperature post-filling, ensuring structural integrity and accelerated set times. Three-roll mills are invaluable for creating ultra-smooth, homogenous textures in creams and pastes.Versatile Packaging and Sealing:Tube filling and sealing systems, compatible with brands like Norden and IWK, make packaging a breeze across various product lines, while soap forming and pen-filling machines expand your portfolio possibilities.Daily Chemical and Skincare Support: Dedicated filling lines for skincare lotions, serums, and fragrance products enable flexible, multi-product manufacturing.When building out your cosmetic facility, these auxiliary machines allow you to scale, customize, and streamline production\\u2014from raw material handling to finished packaging\\u2014all while maintaining quality and efficiency.\"}}]}<\/script>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Lipstick Filling Machine The Lipstick Filling Machine is a type of volumetric dosing equipment for dosing Lipsticks, lip balms, and lip glosses into tubes, molds, or containers. It can be made in semi automatic or fully automatic system. According to users URS, Npack can engineer both of the lipstick filling machine for you. When it [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5113,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[48],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-5047","page","type-page","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail